# Phase Execution Rules

## Phase order (never skip, never reorder)
1. Docker + Databases
2. Legacy openclaw-mission-control (**optional** — skip; Command Center + Control Plane are canonical)
3. OpenClaw Gateway
4. LobsterBoard
5. Ollama + GPU (`qwen3:4b` default)
6. Composio
7. Phone Access + Firewall
8. End-to-End Testing

## Phase gate rule
Do not start the next phase until the verify script for the
current phase exits with code 0. If it fails, fix the issue
in the current phase before proceeding.

## After each phase
1. Run the verify script
2. Confirm all checks pass
3. Mark phase complete in DEPLOYMENT_STATUS.md
4. Print "Phase X complete. Starting Phase X+1." before continuing
